  (descr "Tactile switch HX 12x12x7.3TPFT-B, SMD-4P, 11.8x11.8mm body, 7.3mm height, vertical actuator, SPST. Source: LCSC C36498966 / EasyEDA datasheet (User-verified 2026-06-11).")
